==English==

===Noun===
'''dibble'''

# A [[pointed]] [[implement]] used to make [[hole]]s in the ground in which to set out plants or to plant seeds. Also known as a [[dibber]].
#(slang) the [[police]] or one or more [[police officer]]s (from the character of Officer Dibble in the Hanna-Barbera cartoon series [[w:Top Cat|Top Cat]])
#:''Watch out lads! Here comes the '''dibble'''!''

===Verb===
'''to dibble'''
# To make holes, or plant seeds, using a dibble

